  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YAR is a fully-fledged open-world RPG, granting you the freedom to go wherever you please and do whatever you like. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Complete captivating <u>quests</u> crafted with heart and soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Will you become a valiant <u>Warrior</u> or a wise <u>Mage</u>? Your faction choice will shape your story’s development.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover <u>secrets</u> and ancient <u>artifacts</u> as you explore vast lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Visit eerie <u>dungeons</u> in search of treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Traverse forests, fields, lakes, swamps, icy mountains, scorched woods, lava lands, and numerous dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Encounter legendary characters from Eastern European folklore and mythology. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Create weapons and armor, practice Alchemy, Cooking, Blacksmithing, Magic Crafting, and many other professions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Learn new skills and abilities with a unique and engaging combat system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Utilize melee weapons, bows, crossbows, scrolls, spells, and enchantments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Level up your character and enhance their attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Pray to the Gods for blessings and gifts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Master the art of fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play the card game \"Koshun,\" participate in fistfights, and compete in archery contests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a magical world and the spirit of the Boreyians! Help the Elders and free the land from evil!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YAR is a fully-fledged open-world RPG, granting you the freedom to go wherever you please and do whatever you like. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Complete captivating <u>quests</u> crafted with heart and soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Will you become a valiant <u>Warrior</u> or a wise <u>Mage</u>? Your faction choice will shape your story’s development.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover <u>secrets</u> and ancient <u>artifacts</u> as you explore vast lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Visit eerie <u>dungeons</u> in search of treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Traverse forests, fields, lakes, swamps, icy mountains, scorched woods, lava lands, and numerous dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Encounter legendary characters from Eastern European folklore and mythology. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Create weapons and armor, practice Alchemy, Cooking, Blacksmithing, Magic Crafting, and many other professions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Learn new skills and abilities with a unique and engaging combat system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Utilize melee weapons, bows, crossbows, scrolls, spells, and enchantments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Level up your character and enhance their attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Pray to the Gods for blessings and gifts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Master the art of fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play the card game \"Koshun,\" participate in fistfights, and compete in archery contests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a magical world and the spirit of the Boreyians! Help the Elders and free the land from evil!</p>",
